      <title>俄罗斯油轮制裁未能阻止船只运送莫斯科石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/russian-tanker-sanctions-fail-to-stop-ships-hauling-moscow-s-oil</link>
